CustomArgumentTemplates.Command: bash -c find $(rustup docs --path | sed -e "s|index\.html|std|") $(rustup docs --path | sed -e "s|index\.html|alloc|") $(rustup docs --path | sed -e "s|index\.html|core|") | grep "\.html" | sed -E -e "s|^(.*)/html/||" -e "s|\.html||" -e "s|/|::|g" -e "s/constant\.|trait\.|struct\.|macro\.|fn\.|keyword\.|primitive\.|type\.|enum\.|union\.|traitalias\.|::index$|^(.*)::all$//" -e "/^$/d"
